                            <comment id="17060130" author="blerer" created="Mon, 16 Mar 2020 11:25:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix looks good. I just believe that we should fix the &lt;tt&gt;AlterTest&lt;/tt&gt; test to not use prepared statements for schema changes by default. I pushed a patch for that &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/56c1b0538e344f030cec622f05b9bb220d93ef9f&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jasonstack&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jasonstack&quot;&gt;jasonstack&lt;/a&gt; If my change looks good to you, I think we should push it at the same time as your fix.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17060138" author="jasonstack" created="Mon, 16 Mar 2020 11:37:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=blerer&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;blerer&quot;&gt;blerer&lt;/a&gt; the commit looks good to me!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17060296" author="blerer" created="Mon, 16 Mar 2020 15:21:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed into trunk at 722d10b2c5999f19f3a912dc2fbaeb71cef65a07&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17063506" author="ifesdjeen" created="Fri, 20 Mar 2020 16:49:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This commit has broken AlterTest. I&apos;ve ninja-commited the fix for trunk here &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/b29af2925cddacb4ab8b429b31917748781fbe5d&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;b29af2925cddacb4ab8b429b31917748781fbe5d&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17063523" author="jasonstack" created="Fri, 20 Mar 2020 16:59:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ifesdjeen&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ifesdjeen&quot;&gt;ifesdjeen&lt;/a&gt;&#160;thanks.. It looks the fix is required for &quot;testCreateSimpleAlterNTSDefaults()&quot; as well..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I previously made &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jasonstack/cassandra/commits/CASSANDRA-15303-trunk-fix&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;a fix&lt;/a&gt; to move `testCreateAlterNetworkTopologyWithDefaults / testCreateSimpleAlterNTSDefaults ` into another class..&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://circleci.com/workflow-run/59ea8e29-df8b-40fd-9cfc-1a8d8b78d3a7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt; unit tests passed, dtest failure is not related..&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
